    "fuzzy_and (Lagrange min polynomial \u2014 Sutra's && operator)",
    "fuzzy_not (Kleene negation \u2014 Sutra's ! operator)",
    "scalar * temperature (element-wise \u2014 Sutra's scalar multiply)",
